[Guest]: Well, for art, the most popular one is Ethereum.

04:06:32.660 --> 04:06:33.660
[Unknown]: Okay.

04:06:33.660 --> 04:06:36.860
[Guest]: And for other uses, the most popular one so far is Bitcoin.

04:06:36.860 --> 04:06:39.540
[Guest]: But there is a lot of stuff on other blockchains also.

